main event: On 16 October 1960, three circular yellowish-white objects were observed moving in formation at approximately 500 mph for about 30 seconds.
interesting points: The objects appeared to be flying in formation,The sighting lasted for about 30 seconds,The objects were observed at a time also noted as 10/16/60 2200,The objects were seen moving in a westerly direction from two P-85's,No physical evidence or photographs of the sighting were reported.
witness description: Military personnel standing on the sidewalk
